(381, 1, '2015-12-28 12:50:14', '2015-12-28 12:50:14', '<div class="headline" style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 48px;">\n<div style="background: #17CBB2; border: 1px solid #17CBB2; padding: 5px 10px;"><span style="color: #cf437d;"><sup><sub><span style="font-size: 26px;"><strong>Functional Testing</strong></span></sub></sup></span></div>\n</div>\n\n<hr />\n\n<div style="page-break-after: always;"><span style="display: none;"> </span></div>\n<p style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin-left: 40px;">Requirements are becoming increasingly vertical focused, demanding strong domain expertise to ensure quality test design and maximum coverage with minimized risk to production.</p>\n<p style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin-left: 40px;">As an independent testing company, we bring strong domain knowledge, technical and test management knowledge. We have proven Functional Testing methodology and Testing framework.</p>\n<p style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin-left: 40px;">Our testing services help software product vendors and business software users to assure that their software is functionally perfect. We begin with an assessment of your application or product objectives and lay out a clearly defined implementation plan for aligning functional testing objectives.</p>\n<p style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin-left: 40px;">We provide complete test coverage right from the Requirement stage to ensure reduced defect rates. Starting with Business Requirement documents(BRD), we produce full-coverage, end-to-end business scenarios to uncover critical defects in your existing system. Our approach involves every assignment from a business user perspective to ensure the system is compliant with all user requirements.</p>\n<p style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin-left: 40px;">Our Functional Testing services consist of the following:</p>\n\n<div style="background: #eee; border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 5px 10px;"><span style="color: #008080;"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong>Functional Testing Coverage:</strong></span></span></div>\n\n<hr />\n\n<div style="page-break-after: always;"><span style="display: none;"> </span></div>\n<ul>\n	<li>End to End Testing: From testing requirements to test execution, with strong reporting and management.</li>\n	<li>Functionality Testing - Feature validation of an entire function or component of your product.</li>\n	<li>System Integration Testing - Product/Application functionality testing in an integrated environment through rigorous component testing and interaction with external systems.</li>\n	<li>User Acceptance Testing - Ensure that the product meets end-customer functional requirements.</li>\n	<li>Regression Testing - Correction of application defects for each new release and ensuring that no new functional problems are introduced.</li>\n	<li>Detailed test reporting at the end of each test cycle</li>\n</ul>\n<div style="background: #eee; border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 5px 10px;"><span style="color: #008080;"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong>Advantage Factor :</strong></span></span></div>\n\n<hr />\n\n<div style="page-break-after: always;"><span style="display: none;"> </span></div>\n<ul>\n	<li>Strong experience in testing delivery of large enterprise applications</li>\n	<li>Proven expertise on product and Professional Services testing projects</li>\n	<li>strong expertise in test strategy, planning and test execution techniques</li>\n	<li>An end-customer focused approach</li>\n	<li>Identification of defects earlier in the development process by left shift approach</li>\n	<li>Efficient testing through the usage of best practices</li>\n	<li>Optimal test coverage</li>\n	<li>Reduction of testing cycles, leading to reduced overall testing costs by test optimization techniques</li>\n</ul>\n<div style="background: #eee; border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 5px 10px;"><span style="color: #008080;"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong>All Test Levels:</strong></span></span></div>\n\n<hr />\n\n<div style="page-break-after: always;"><span style="display: none;"> </span></div>\n<p style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin-left: 40px;">Software development is a highly complex, time-consuming and cost-intensive process. If an IT system fails, it costs future business, funds, reputation and customers.</p>\n<p style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin-left: 40px;">The sources of errors are both annoying and varied; misunderstandings at the design stage, program errors or unforeseen project conditions.</p>\n<p style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin-left: 40px;">The TBS testing experts use functional testing on all test levels to test your software thoroughly and eliminate errors early in the design and development stage.</p>\n<p style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin-left: 40px;">This means that you can benefit from our years of experience of preparing, running and managing functional tests.</p>\n<p style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin-left: 40px;">Starting as early as with component testing supporting developers, via integration testing , system testing, system integration testing, up to complex business process testing like end to end testing from user perspective.</p>', 'Functional Testing', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'functional-testing', '', '', '2015-12-28 12:50:14', '2015-12-28 12:50:14', '', 0, 'http://www.techbodhi.co.in/?page_id=381', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(386, 1, '2015-12-28 13:11:59', '2015-12-28 13:11:59', '<div class="headline" style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 48px;">\n<div style="background: #17CBB2; border: 1px solid #17CBB2; padding: 5px 10px;"><span style="color: #cf437d;"><sup><sub><span style="font-size: 26px;"><strong>Non Functional Testing</strong></span></sub></sup></span></div>\n</div>\n\n<hr />\n\n<div style="page-break-after: always;"><span style="display: none;"> </span></div>\n<div style="page-break-after: always;"><span style="display: none;"> </span></div>\n<div style="page-break-after: always;"><span style="display: none;"> </span></div>\n<p style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin-left: 40px;">We provide various Non-Functional Testing services to customers. We bring strong experience in most industry standard tools and are capable of providing testing services across various technologies. Our Non-Functional Testing services span the following:</p>\n\n<div style="background: #eee; border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 5px 10px;"><span style="color: #008080;"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong>Performance and Load Testing</strong></span></span></div>\n\n<hr />\n<p style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin-left: 40px;">TBS  support you with load and performance tests, in order to help you provide your users with the best possible service. Our performance experts develop conclusive test cases based on realistic scenarios, in order to assess how users have experienced your system.</p>\n<p style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin-left: 40px;"><strong>Service Offerings</strong></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Load Testing</span></li>\n	<li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Stress Testing</span></li>\n	<li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Volume Testing</span></li>\n	<li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Soak Testing</span></li>\n	<li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Scalability Testing and Capacity Planning</span></li>\n	<li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Profiling</span></li>\n</ol>\n<div style="background: #eee; border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 5px 10px;"><span style="color: #008080;"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong>Security Testing :</strong></span></span></div>\n<ol>\n	<li><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="line-height: 1.6em;"><strong>Assesment: </strong>We assess your applications, by analysing requirements, architecture and source code</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>Testing: </strong>Dynamic tests detect security gaps, e.g. by automated testing of interfaces</span></li>\n	<li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Penetration testing of applications and IT infrastructure</span></li>\n	<li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Training for teams in secure software development</span></li>\n	<li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Preparation of mandatory concepts for secure application development</span></li>\n	<li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Evaluation and adjustment of suitable tools</span></li>\n	<li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Definition of processes, information flows and how results are presented</span></li>\n	<li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Establishment of a semi or fully-automated quality gate for the technical acceptance of software</span></li>\n	<li><span style="font-size: 14px;">Assist with the definition of IT Security Management systems (ITSMS), e.g. in compliance with ISO 27000 or BSI Baseline Protection</span></li>\n</ol>\n<div style="background: #eee; border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 5px 10px;"><span style="color: #008080;"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong>Compatibility Testing:</strong></span></span></div>\n<div style="page-break-after: always;"><span style="display: none;"> </span></div>\n\n<hr />\n<p style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin-left: 40px;">In today’s world, end users can choose from a number of browsers, operating systems and technology stacks and it is expected that the applications they use are compatible with these. Compatibility Testing helps in verifying that the applications work as expected across different browsers, operating systems and technology stacks.</p>\n<p style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin-left: 40px;">TBS provides Compatibility or Porting Testing services that can be performed across a variety of Operating Systems, browsers, databases, servers, hardware, different versions, configurations, display resolutions etc.</p>\n<p style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin-left: 40px;"> Whether you produce software product, online applications, websites, network software or utilities, our compatibility services can build a configuration matrix and methodology to identify the optimum number of combinations.</p>', 'Non Functional Testing', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'non-functional-testing', '', '', '2015-12-28 13:11:59', '2015-12-28 13:11:59', '', 0, 'http://www.techbodhi.co.in/?page_id=386', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(389, 1, '2015-12-28 13:12:24', '2015-12-28 13:12:24', '<div style="background: #17CBB2; border: 1px solid #17CBB2; padding: 5px 10px;"><span style="color: #cf437d;"><span style="font-size: 26px;"><b>Enterprise Application Testing</b></span></span></div>\n<p style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin-left: 40px;">Any Enterprise application implementation program, whether big or small, be it an upgrade, replacement or a change of technology platform will always be a complex process. We support banks and companies achieve aggressive timelines and quality levels in their enterprise application roll-outs through structured requirements validation followed by component testing, system testing, integration testing, user acceptance testing, test automation, security testing and performance testing services.</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 5px 20px; background: url(\'images/0003.png\') 1px 5px no-repeat;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">We guarantee at least a 25-30% reduction on testing timelines</span></li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 5px 20px; background: url(\'images/0003.png\') 1px 5px no-repeat;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">We ensure early validation through High Risk Functionality Tests (HRFT)</span></li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 5px 20px; background: url(\'images/0003.png\') 1px 5px no-repeat;"><span style="font-size: 16px; background-color: initial;">Our unique test defination team, enables comprehensive test coverage by writing an optimized set of cases</span></li>\n</ul>\n<div style="background: #17CBB2; border: 1px solid #17CBB2; padding: 5px 10px;"><span style="color: #cf437d;"><span style="font-size: 26px;"><b>Multi Channel Testing</b></span></span></div>\n<p style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin-left: 40px;">Banks and financial institutions are leveraging the immense power and reach of technology to offer their wide arrays of products and services online. Internet has become a favored platform for reaching out to clients worldwide, and for conducting business effectively by overcoming the constraints of time and resources.</p>\n<p style="font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin-left: 40px;">Web based applications are increasingly becoming more feature rich, important and also the most popular means for developing commercial systems. Most companies opt for developing web based software wherever possible. This helps in catering to large number of end users. Once the required infrastructure is in place, the deployment of the apps is fairly easy.</p>\n<p style="padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 8px 40px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #353535; line-height: 17px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">The channel based applications are powerful and have the ability to provide feature rich content to a wide audience spread across the globe at an economical cost.</span></p>\n<p style="padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 8px 40px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #353535; line-height: 17px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">Hence multi-channel applications are required to exhibit high performance levels, interactivity, security and speed. Interoperability of applications across various platforms, browsers, servers and languages is critical. Additionally, increased customer usage means that these applications have to adhere to usability and performance standards set by the bank. Rising instances of Internet fraud demand that these systems are made secure and are protected from unauthenticated/unauthorized users.</span></p>\n&nbsp;\n<div id="immer" class="first" style="border: 1px solid #cccccc; padding: 5px 10px; margin-left: 40px; background: #eeeeee;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><strong><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Challenges faced in Multi-Channel Testing</span></strong></span></div>\n<div id="onOffFirst" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #353535; line-height: 17px;">\n<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><em><span style="font-size: 16px;">Testing web applications is different because of many factors and scenarios affecting the performance and user experience. Web applications can typically accommodate large and different audiences. Following are the challenges faced in testing multi-channel applications:</span></em></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Synchronisation of test data across channels and back-end hosts in a test environment</span></span></li>\n	<li style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Simulation of external/third party interface files/messages for bill payments, fund transfers, mobile payments and more</span></span></li>\n	<li style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Ensuring sufficient test coverage to provide a secured and safety reliable application to the end user should consider factors such as</span></span>\n<ol>\n	<li style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Availability of numerous application usage paths</span></span></li>\n	<li style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Different background and different technical skills of end users Internet versus Intranet based applications</span></span></li>\n	<li style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Validation of tests across multiple browsers</span></span></li>\n	<li style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Regulatory compliance and usability</span></span></li>\n	<li style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Security measures</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>', 'Enterprise Application Testing', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'enterprise-application-testing', '', '', '2015-12-28 13:12:24', '2015-12-28 13:12:24', '', 0, 'http://www.techbodhi.co.in/?page_id=389', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(392, 1, '2015-12-28 13:12:43', '2015-12-28 13:12:43', '<div id="tabs">\n<h2>Need for Mobile Application Testing</h2>\nEnterprises are using mobile technology as a \'Game Changer\' to increase operational efficiency &amp; accelerate business growth. The productivity gain offered by mobile applications is propelling the immediate need for an enterprise wide mobile strategy.There are several challenges at all stages including conceptualization, design, development, testing and deployment. The business shorter time to-market and the users demanding device &amp; version proof applications are not making things any easier for product managers.\n\n</div>\n<div id="tabs">\n<ul>\n	<li class="tabs_article">\n<h3>Key Challenges</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\nThere are several factors that make <strong>mobile application testing</strong> even more challenging than testing desktop &amp; web applications. Some of the hurdles include platform fragmentation, high user expectations, security, performance &amp; integration issues.<strong> Mobile apps/applications testing</strong> therefore must adopt a far more robust approach.\n<ul>\n	<li class="tabs_article">\n<h3>Our Mobile Testing Services</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\nTech Bodhi adopts a business-driven testing approach covering all aspects of mobile app development from conceptualization to app certification, focusing on the business and user\'s satisfiers from the start. The Centre of Mobility Excellence at Tech Bodhi (CoME) delivers managed test services that bring together best in class expertise, processes, tools and infrastructure to help customers roll out secure &amp; engaging apps.\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n	<li class="tabs_article">\n<h3>Mobile Test Automation</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\nAt Tech Bodhi, a dedicated group of mobile test automation specialists focus on identifying and applying traditional and mobile-focused emerging automation tools. Our automation specialist group includes dedicated automation test architects and implementation engineers who cover the length of automation testing tools across the breadth of mobile platforms.\n<ul class="topbullet">\n	<li class="tabs_a">\n<h3>Key Differentiators</h3>\n</li>\n	<li>In-depth domain knowledge in specific business application testing such as Mobile CRM, Product Catalogs, Collaboration Platforms, eLearning, Social Media, Analytics &amp; Dashboards</li>\n	<li>CoME is equipped with several generations of physical devices inc. J2ME, Blackberry Brew, Windows mobile,iOS, Android phones and tablets</li>\n	<li>Automation tool capabilities include Monkey Talk, Calabash, Selenium, Robotium &amp; UI Automation amongst others</li>\n	<li>A powerful test methodology, employing automation techniques and workflow management tools for helps address remote access challenges, simulate network conditions, test scripts reuse and automation Tech Bodhi. Cloud based testing empowers developers and testers, located around the globe, to access a comprehensive range of the latest mobile handsets and tablets</li>\n	<li>Trained &amp; ISTQB certified experts can handle complex testing engagements</li>\n	<li>Waterproof delivery methods ensure alignment to development, meeting quality targets, manage timelines &amp; costs</li>\n</ul>\n</div>', 'Mobility Testing', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mobility-testing', '', '', '2015-12-28 13:12:43', '2015-12-28 13:12:43', '', 0, 'http://www.techbodhi.co.in/?page_id=392', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(395, 1, '2015-12-28 13:12:55', '2015-12-28 13:12:55', '<h3><strong>Game Functional Testing</strong></h3>\nTech Bodhi provides game functional test services for major studios and independent developers, from cost-effective test centers in the Americas, Europe, and Asia. Our test teams can scale up from two to two hundred testers and test leads, and can flex to meet release and seasonal demands. Available services include:\n<ul>\n	<li>Top compliance problem areas</li>\n	<li>Game balance testing</li>\n	<li>User experience testing</li>\n	<li>Stability and performance</li>\n	<li>Content verification</li>\n	<li>Play-through testing</li>\n	<li>Multiplayer testing</li>\n	<li>Core features and functionality</li>\n	<li>Destructive testing</li>\n	<li>Device compatibility</li>\n</ul>\nAnd we can do it all for you with one point of contact for fewer touch points and a faster, smoother experience.\n\n&nbsp;', 'Game Testing', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'game-testing', '', '', '2015-12-28 13:12:55', '2015-12-28 13:12:55', '', 0, 'http://www.techbodhi.co.in/?page_id=395', 0, 'page', '', 0),
